namespace = ehof_category

# Short handed all options for performance reasons
# a4_c01	= allow_phase4_category_01
# c4_c01	= cost_phase4_category_01
# s_c01		= star_category_01
# un_c01	= unexplored_category_01
# ex_c01	= explored_category_01

# Point of Interest
country_event = {
	id = ehof_category.01
	title = "ehof_category_01"
	desc = {
		trigger = {
			check_variable = { which = ehof_phase value = 4 }
			NOR = {
				check_variable = { which = ehof_acc_true value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_acc_false value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_nogo value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_debris value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_detonated value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_damaged value > 0 }
			}
		}
		text = "ehof_megastructure.301_04_desc"
	}
	desc = {
		trigger = {
			check_variable = { which = ehof_phase value = 4 }
			OR = {
				check_variable = { which = ehof_acc_true value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_acc_false value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_nogo value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_debris value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_detonated value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_damaged value > 0 }
			}
		}
		text = "ehof_megastructure.301_14_desc"
	}
	custom_gui = "ehof_mainui_window"
	is_triggered_only = yes
	diplomatic = yes
	picture_event_data = {
		portrait = root.owner
		room = root.owner.ruler
		planet_background = root.owner 
		graphical_culture = root.owner
		city_level = root.owner
	}
	location = event_target:ehof_megastructure_system
	immediate = { ehof_mega_system = yes }

	option = {
		custom_gui = "enclave_ehof_ehof_header"
		name = "ehof_header_04"
		hidden_effect = { country_event = { id = ehof_category.01 } }
		trigger = {
			any_system = {
				OR = {
					is_same_value = event_target:s_c01_001
					is_same_value = event_target:s_c01_003
				}
				ehof_visited = no
			}
		}
	}
	option = { custom_gui = "ehof_mainui_option" allow = { a4_c01 = yes } c4_c01 = yes trigger = { exists = event_target:s_c01_001 event_target:s_c01_001 = { ehof_visited = no } } name = "un_c01.001" hidden_effect = { event_target:s_c01_001 = { p4_go = yes } } }
	option = { custom_gui = "ehof_mainui_option" allow = { a4_c01 = yes } c4_c01 = yes trigger = { exists = event_target:s_c01_003 event_target:s_c01_003 = { ehof_visited = no } } name = "un_c01.003" hidden_effect = { event_target:s_c01_003 = { p4_go = yes } } }
	option = { custom_gui = "enclave_ehof_ehof_header" name = "ehof_header_blank"	hidden_effect = { country_event = { id = ehof_category.01 } } trigger = { any_system =  { has_star_flag = ehof_advanced_resources ehof_visited = yes } } }



	option = {
		custom_gui = "enclave_ehof_ehof_header"
		name = "ehof_header_05"
		hidden_effect = { country_event = { id = ehof_category.01 } }
		trigger = {
			any_system = {
				OR = {
					is_same_value = event_target:s_c01_001
					is_same_value = event_target:s_c01_003
				}
				ehof_visited = yes
			}
		}
	}
	option = { custom_gui = "ehof_mainui_option" allow = { a4_c01 = yes } c4_c01 = yes trigger = { exists = event_target:s_c01_001 event_target:s_c01_001 = { ehof_visited = yes } } name = "ex_c01.001" hidden_effect = { event_target:s_c01_001 = { p4_go = yes } } }
	option = { custom_gui = "ehof_mainui_option" allow = { a4_c01 = yes } c4_c01 = yes trigger = { exists = event_target:s_c01_003 event_target:s_c01_003 = { ehof_visited = yes } } name = "ex_c01.003" hidden_effect = { event_target:s_c01_003 = { p4_go = yes } } }

	option = { custom_gui = "enclave_ehof_ehof_header" name = "ehof_header_blank"	hidden_effect = { country_event = { id = ehof_category.01 } } }
	option = { custom_gui = "enclave_ehof_ehof_header" name = "ehof_header_03"		hidden_effect = { country_event = { id = ehof_category.01 } } }
	option = { custom_gui = "ehof_mainui_option" name = "ehof_goback" ehof_go_back = yes }
	option = { custom_gui = "ehof_mainui_option" name = "ehof_leavestation" ehof_leave_station = yes default_hide_option = yes }
}

# Bountiful Stars (200)
country_event = {
	id = ehof_category.02
	title = "ehof_category_02"
	desc = {
		trigger = {
			check_variable = { which = ehof_phase value = 4 }
			NOR = {
				check_variable = { which = ehof_acc_true value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_acc_false value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_nogo value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_debris value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_detonated value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_damaged value > 0 }
			}
		}
		text = "ehof_megastructure.301_04_desc"
	}
	desc = {
		trigger = {
			check_variable = { which = ehof_phase value = 4 }
			OR = {
				check_variable = { which = ehof_acc_true value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_acc_false value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_nogo value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_debris value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_detonated value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_damaged value > 0 }
			}
		}
		text = "ehof_megastructure.301_14_desc"
	}
	custom_gui = "ehof_mainui_window"
	is_triggered_only = yes
	diplomatic = yes
	picture_event_data = {
		portrait = root.owner
		room = root.owner.ruler
		planet_background = root.owner
		graphical_culture = root.owner
		city_level = root.owner
	}

		ehof_mega_system = yes
	}

	option = { custom_gui = "enclave_ehof_ehof_header" name = "ehof_header_04"		hidden_effect = { country_event = { id = ehof_category.02 } } trigger = { any_system =  { has_star_flag = ehof_advanced_resources ehof_visited = no } } }

# Wormhole Cohesive (500)
country_event = {
	id = ehof_category.03
	title = "ehof_category_03"
	desc = {
		trigger = {
			check_variable = { which = ehof_phase value = 4 }
			NOR = {
				check_variable = { which = ehof_acc_true value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_acc_false value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_nogo value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_debris value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_detonated value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_damaged value > 0 }
			}
		}
		text = "ehof_megastructure.301_04_desc"
	}
	desc = {
		trigger = {
			check_variable = { which = ehof_phase value = 4 }
			OR = {
				check_variable = { which = ehof_acc_true value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_acc_false value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_nogo value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_debris value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_detonated value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_damaged value > 0 }
			}
		}
		text = "ehof_megastructure.301_14_desc"
	}
	custom_gui = "ehof_mainui_window"
	is_triggered_only = yes
	diplomatic = yes
	picture_event_data = {
		portrait = root.owner
		room = root.owner.ruler
		planet_background = root.owner
		graphical_culture = root.owner
		city_level = root.owner
	}
	location = event_target:ehof_megastructure_system
	immediate = { ehof_mega_system = yes }

	option = { custom_gui = "enclave_ehof_ehof_header" name = "ehof_header_04"		hidden_effect = { country_event = { id = ehof_category.03 } } trigger = { any_system = { NOT = { has_star_flag = ehof_advanced_resources } ehof_cohesive_system = yes ehof_visited = no } } }

	id = ehof_category.05
	title = "ehof_category_05"
	desc = {
		trigger = {
			check_variable = { which = ehof_phase value = 4 }
			NOR = {
				check_variable = { which = ehof_acc_true value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_acc_false value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_nogo value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_debris value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_detonated value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_damaged value > 0 }
			}
		}
		text = "ehof_megastructure.301_04_desc"
	}
	desc = {
		trigger = {
			check_variable = { which = ehof_phase value = 4 }
			OR = {
				check_variable = { which = ehof_acc_true value > 0 }

				check_variable = { which = ehof_nogo value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_debris value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_detonated value > 0 }

# Trinary Stars (125)
country_event = {
	id = ehof_category.07
	title = "ehof_category_07"
	desc = {
		trigger = {
			check_variable = { which = ehof_phase value = 4 }
			NOR = {
				check_variable = { which = ehof_acc_true value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_acc_false value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_nogo value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_debris value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_detonated value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_damaged value > 0 }
			}
		}
		text = "ehof_megastructure.301_04_desc"
	}
	desc = {
		trigger = {
			check_variable = { which = ehof_phase value = 4 }
			OR = {
				check_variable = { which = ehof_acc_true value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_acc_false value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_nogo value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_debris value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_detonated value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_damaged value > 0 }
			}
		}
		text = "ehof_megastructure.301_14_desc"
	}

# Fledgling Stars (100)

	id = ehof_category.09
	title = "ehof_category_09"
	desc = {
		trigger = {
			check_variable = { which = ehof_phase value = 4 }
			NOR = {
				check_variable = { which = ehof_acc_true value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_acc_false value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_nogo value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_debris value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_detonated value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_damaged value > 0 }
			}
		}
		text = "ehof_megastructure.301_04_desc"
	}
	desc = {
		trigger = {
			check_variable = { which = ehof_phase value = 4 }
			OR = {
				check_variable = { which = ehof_acc_true value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_acc_false value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_nogo value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_debris value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_detonated value > 0 }

			check_variable = { which = ehof_phase value = 4 }
			NOR = {
				check_variable = { which = ehof_acc_true value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_acc_false value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_nogo value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_debris value > 0 }
				check_variable = { which = ehof_stats_detonated value > 0 }
